<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <title>BusEaze - Online Bus Reservation System</title>
    <link href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/5.15.3/css/all.min.css" rel="stylesheet" />
    <script src="https://kit.fontawesome.com/e1d08f83d4.js" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="css/main.css" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="css/navbar.css" />
</head>
<body>

<nav class="navbar">
    <div class="logo">
        <h2><a href="/main" style="text-decoration: none; color:antiquewhite">BusEase</a></h2>
    </div>
    <ul id="navbar-links" class="nav__menu">
        <li class="dropdown">
            <a href="#" class="dropbtn">Login/Signup <i class="fas fa-caret-down"></i></a>
            <div class="dropdown-content">
                <a href="/login">Login</a>
                <a href="/register">Signup</a>
            </div>
        </li>
    </ul>
</nav>


    <!-- Hero Section -->
    <section id="hero" class="hero">
        <div class="hero-content">
            <h1>Your Journey Starts Here</h1>
            <p>Discover top bus routes across the country and book your tickets effortlessly.</p>
            <div class="hero-buttons">
                <a href="/register" class="btn btn-signup">Sign Up</a>
                <a href="/login" class="btn btn-login">Login in</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Popular Destinations -->
    <section id="popular-destinations" class="popular-destinations">
        <h2>Popular Bus Travel Destinations</h2>
        <p>Here are some of the most popular cities you can travel to by bus. Choose your next adventure!</p>

        <div class="destination-grid">
            <div class="destination-card">
                <img src="https://th.bing.com/th/id/R.d6361bf60474d0bebd0163df5fe9d35d?rik=0UaPDSoqHhmX%2fw&riu=http%3a%2f%2fwww.bhavyaholidays.com%2fblogs%2fwp-content%2fuploads%2f2014%2f03%2fQutub-Minar-Delhi.jpg&ehk=jWlKgqANH%2fF%2bw6HhyTVcTSv5SvBoOfR%2b6%2faLVNTUoto%3d&risl=&pid=ImgRaw&r=0" alt="Delhi">
                <h3>Delhi</h3>
                <p>Explore the historical capital of India, known for its iconic monuments such as the Red Fort, India Gate, and the bustling markets of Chandni Chowk.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="destination-card">
                <img src="https://i0.wp.com/imgmedia.lbb.in/media/2019/02/5c598dfe866c8e7f31e07041_1549372926458.jpg" alt="Goa">
                <h3>Goa</h3>
                <p>Famous for its pristine beaches and vibrant nightlife, Goa offers a mix of relaxation and adventure for beach lovers and partygoers alike.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="destination-card">
                <img src="https://th.bing.com/th/id/OIP.TnxOV8RDWZY3y5QTOHipDQHaGb?rs=1&pid=ImgDetMain" alt="Mumbai">
                <h3>Mumbai</h3>
                <p>The city that never sleeps, Mumbai is the financial hub of India, offering a blend of traditional culture and modern living.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="destination-card">
                <img src="https://i.pinimg.com/originals/71/d1/24/71d1242b021638b90de4f68a674fd451.jpg" alt="Jaipur">
                <h3>Jaipur</h3>
                <p>The Pink City of Jaipur is known for its majestic palaces, vibrant bazaars, and historical forts, offering a royal experience in the heart of Rajasthan.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <footer class="footer">
        <div class="footer-container">
            <p>&copy; 2024 BusEase. All rights reserved.</p>
            <ul class="footer-links">
                <li><a href="/terms">Terms and Conditions</a></li>
                <li><a href="/privacy">Privacy Policy</a></li>
                <li><a href="/contact">Contact Us</a></li>
            </ul>
        </div>
    </footer>

    <script src="js/script.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
